::KitKat::

She looked down, wishing she could give a different answer than the 
one she was about to say."No, no chance. They have been allies for 
some time. They trust each other. No matter how you try to divied 
them, they still fight side by side."  She looked down and sighed 
softly. She knew that with a team like this one that stood before 
her, they would go with the more powerful group. Her's wasn't as 
power as the Allience. But she hoped that soon, she would be as power 
ful and defeat the Allience.
